  <h1>Joel Farland</h1>
  <h4>Independent</h4>
  <p>Joel plays:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>14&quot; Traditional Medium Light Hat (top) 14&quot; Rude (Bottom)</li>
    <li>20&quot; Traditional Light Ride</li>
    <li>24&quot; Giant Beat</li>
